# Title: PSExec and WMI Process Creations Block
# Author: Bhabesh Raj
# Date: 2020-07-14
# Level: high
# Description: Detects blocking of process creations originating from PSExec and WMI commands
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.lateral-movement, attack.t1047, attack.t1569.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/windefend/win_defender_asr_psexec_wmi.yml

EventID=1121 ProcessName IN ("*\\wmiprvse.exe", "*\\psexesvc.exe")